"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_1\"&gt;Business flows&lt;/a&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;a href=\"#\" data-oe-nodeid=\"12\" "
"class=\"o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link "
"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2\"&gt;🎁 ​Loyalty program&lt;/a&gt;\n"
"                        &lt;a href=\"#\" data-oe-nodeid=\"13\" "
"class=\"o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link "
"o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_3\"&gt;Demo: Sell in-store and give your customer "
